Prism, ups, pcis, spcs - Release 1

add emms,vipers, etc - Release 2

Developer Notes:

Material Assignment:


Data Summarization:
Implementation of this feature can vary. There could be a database table that calculates line items and stores the result per contract. Or, there could be a database view which automatically sums items.  The choice would be depend on the volume of data and performance.

Results.Description:
as a responsible person I need to be notified when any new property items are added to my list so I don't overlook them

system identifies newly assigned items, since original or last new item notification, and sends an email to the affected RP

  • new items appear in list with 'new' flag
  • flag remains until manually cleared by user
    • only assigned responsible person can clear
  • user can specify to see/have flagged all items added since a user entered date
  • 30 day time window applied to each new item


Developer Notes:

System will need to keep track of items via a daily snapshot. A java cron job could run after data has been loaded to indicate which items are new.

Who tracks changes in data fields? Business analysts or app dev?
Results.Name: RP new item notification
